title: Blumentals WeBuilder 2016 14.1.0.185
description:
Blumentals WeBuilder 2016 14.1.0.185

About this release

Release date: 6/6/2016
Language: multilingual
Installation: run setup, do not launch the app, copy cracked file to installation directory and overwrite existing file, launch application and enter any data to register

About Blumentals WeBuilder

WeBuilder is a faster, smarter and more powerful all-in-one code editor for web developers. Clean interface, quick startup, superb flexibility and powerful features allow you to create and manage code written in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PHP, Ruby, Python, ASP, SSI, Perl and other languages faster and easier, while integrated tools enable you to validate, reuse, navigate and deploy your code in an efficient and sophisticated manner.

Features

Super quick - Loads much faster than any other code editor or IDE with similar features
HTML5 and CSS3 ready - Coding features are up-to-date with modern standards
Fully-packed HTML & CSS editor - HTML & CSS editor with auto complete, inspector, code assistants and more
Powerful syntax highlighting - Supports HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PHP, XML, ASP, ASP.Net, C#.Net, Perl, Python, Ruby, SQL, Apache and more
Direct FTP/SFTP/FTPS - Edit directly on your web server or publish local development copy updates with a single click
Fully-packed PHP editor -PHP editor with auto complete, syntax check, debugger, beautifier and more
Full Unicode support -Supports UTF-8 with and without BOM as well as UTF-16
Smart code re-use -Code snippet library and code templates with assignable shortcuts
Fully-packed JavaScript editor -JavaScript code editor with auto complete, language tools and more
Code intelligence - Tons of intelligent code completion, navigation and suggestion features
Advanced search and replace -Quick search, detailed search, file search, regular expression support, detailed results and more
Integrated validation & debugging -Spell checker, W3 HTML and CSS validator, JSLint JavaScript checker, realtime PHP checker, xDebug PHP debugger

Homepage http://www.webuilderapp.com/
